 mainContainer documentContainer postContainer homepageCustom bannerCustom"><div class="wrapper"><div class="containerBlockBanner"><div class="imageSectionBanner"><a href="https://events.centreon.com/centreon-summit-2021?utm_source=CentreonSummit_Website&amp;utm_campaign=CentreonSummit2021" target="_blank"><div class="imageContainer"><img src="./img/homepage/summit-banner-en.png"/></div></a></div></div></div></div><div class="container mainContainer documentContainer postContainer homepageCustom homepageCustom"><div class="wrapper"><div class="containerBlockPrerequisite"><div class="imageSectionPrerequisite"><div class="imageContainer"><img src="./img/homepage/image-prerequisite-block.svg"/></div></div><div class="containerContentPrerequisite"><h2 class="titleSection">Prerequisites</h2><p>We provide a software appliance complete with its Linux Operating System, Databases or Web Server. Install Centreon on a virtual or physical server. Read this chapter to understand<a href="installation/prerequisites.html"> dimensioning guidelines </a>and distributed architectures.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="container mainContainer documentContainer postContainer homepageCustom bgLightBlue"><div class="wrapper"><div class="containerBlockInstallation"><div class="imageSectionInstallation"><div class="imageContainer"><img src="./img/homepage/image-installation-block.svg"/></div></div><div class="containerContentInstallation"><h2 class="titleSection">Installing</h2><p>You may install Centreon from its ISO image or from an OVA file. Read this chapter and follow the<a href="installation/introduction.html"> step-by-step procedure</a>.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="container mainContainer documentContainer postContainer homepageCustom homepageCustom"><div class="wrapper"><div class="containerBlockMonitoring"><div class="imageSectionMonitoring"><div class="imageContainer"><img src="./img/homepage/image-monitoring-block.svg"/></div></div><div class="containerContentMonitoring"><h2 class="titleSection">Monitoring from Cloud-to-Edge</h2><p>Monitoring should be that easy: we packaged everything you need for 1-click setup into a library of 400+ Enterprise Plugin Packs. Find here<a href="integrations/plugin-packs/introduction.html"> which KPIs are monitored </a>by each one of them.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="container mainContainer documentContainer postContainer homepageCustom borderTop"><div class="wrapper"><div class="containerBlock"><h2 class="titleSectionCommunity">A strong community</h2><div class="cardBar"><ul class="socialSet"><a href="https://centreon.github.io/register-slack/" target="_blank"><li><div class="imageContainer"><img src="./img/homepage/social-network/slack.svg"/></div></li></a><a href="https://github.com/centreon/centreon/" target="_blank"><li><div class="imageContainer"><img src="./img/homepage/social-network/github.svg"/></div></li></a><a href="https://twitter.com/CentreonFR/" target="_blank"><li><div class="imageContainer"><img src="./img/homepage/social-network/twitter.svg"/></div></li></a><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/merethis/" target="_blank"><li><div class="imageContainer"><img src="./img/homepage/social-network/linkedin.svg"/></div></li></a></ul></div></div></div></div><div class="container mainContainer documentContainer postContainer homepageCustom bgLightPurple"><div class="wrapper"><div class="containerBlock"><div class="containerContentOpenSource"><h2 class="titleSectionOpenSource">An Open Source Core</h2><p class="textOpenSource">Praised by hundreds of thousands of IT professionals around the world with 6,000 monthly downloads, Centreon has become the number 1 in open source monitoring in Europe.</p></div><div class="cardBarOpenSource"><div class="cardContent"><div class="imageContainer"><img src="./img/homepage/icon-openSource.svg"/></div><div class="pluginWrapper buttonWrapper"><a class="button buttonLink" href="https://github.com/centreon/centreon/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.